{"tid":1986034,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"FF7蒂法克勞德「啪啪真相」曝光 玩家看完崩潰：小時候沒上到車","createTime":"2020-04-23T14:24:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-26T16:53:58.000Z","uid":25345,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"32af12b288044d6b8da313ddb6f764f4dc7f160d","tid":1986034,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T14:24:01.000Z","msg":"（警告：本文含1997年版《太空戰士7》劇情雷，請謹慎閱讀）<br />\n<br />\n拿著大刀對抗神羅電力公司，甚至相遇兩大女主角艾麗絲、蒂法，1997年經典遊戲《太空戰士7》讓不少玩家化身中二男主角克勞德，享受著刺激冒險與男女間感情糾葛。<br />\n<br />\n隨著《太空戰士7：重製版》推出後，許多玩家重溫了當年的感動，讓全球玩家又開始當起了「黃髮渣男」，邁向解救世界的道路。但由於《太空戰士7：重製版》只收入了一部分序章的內容，後面的遊戲還尚未推出，這也讓許多老玩家開始議論紛紛後面的劇情，之後到底「會重製成甚麼樣子」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/1500/1500454.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F1500%2F1500454.jpg&h=1a25e091&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但近期一篇討論劇情的文章，卻讓許多玩家崩潰了，有玩家就問到敏感話題「蒂法與克勞德在1997年版本有啪啪啪嗎？」，隨後還貼上了1997年「方塊人版」FF7遊戲畫面配上中文翻譯字幕，原來在最終決戰前，玩家只要滿足特定條件（好感度夠高），就能開啟與蒂法的神祕對話：<br />\n<br />\n蒂法：「只有我們兩個，沒有家可以回，也沒有甚麼人在等著我們...但只要和克勞德在一起，只要有克勞德陪在我身邊，我...」<br />\n<br />\n克勞德：「現在你就在我身邊，可是我卻不知道該說些甚麼...」<br />\n<br />\n蒂法：「想告訴別人你在想甚麼，不一定要透過語言」（畫面漸暗）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/pMrL3Sal.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FpMrL3Sal.jpg&h=e00366b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/aFsOTjgl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FaFsOTjgl.jpg&h=66b94145&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/xvnFl2Il.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FxvnFl2Il.jpg&h=e3a44430&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/9BOmG21l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F9BOmG21l.jpg&h=cb53abd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n（到了早上）<br />\n蒂法：「早安．．．克勞德。」「這樣的日子，也許再也不會有了，所以讓我擁有這一刻吧。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ZowMl61l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FZowMl61l.jpg&h=0b93c198&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（回到船上）<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/jE2d3ILl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FjE2d3ILl.jpg&h=10b5d2ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n蒂法：「回來不用講一聲的嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n同伴：「要事先跟你們講我們回來了，就沒好戲看了」<br />\n<br />\n（隨即蒂法爆頭崩潰在旁邊）<br />\n<br />\n  <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/1wYrCfql.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F1wYrCfql.jpg&h=9f7510b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/VeTI00El.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FVeTI00El.jpg&h=431603de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/p6tHkEWl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fp6tHkEWl.jpg&h=53517e25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n．<br />\n．<br />\n．<br />\n看到了這段遊戲影片，許多玩家紛紛崩潰留言，「為什麼我小時候沒這段」「我的童年被毀了+1」「這個意思是他們在打野砲嗎？」「自己當年沒啪到，看到別人說有啪到還一副理所當然的樣子，當然崩潰」「當年才國小，又是日文誰會看的懂阿」<br />\n<br />\nFF7蒂法克勞德「啪啪真相」曝光 玩家看完崩潰：小時候沒上到車（圖／遊戲《FF7RE》截圖）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4832/4832937.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4832%2F4832937.jpg&h=e7284cdc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原來在當年的遊戲訪談中，製作人北賴佳範與劇本野島一成就提到了當年礙於遊戲平台，沒辦法做的很露骨「原本是想要做的更明顯的，自然一點，但最後就只能這樣」製作人如此說著，而這個訪談可說是官方證實了克勞德與蒂法的「啪啪真相」到底如何。<br />\n<br />\n隨著《重製版》的推出，不少老玩家就接著討論這段最後的「隱藏劇情」到底會怎麼重現遊戲之中，「贊成最後分成人版與普版」，但是一想到史克威爾以前光是出《FFXIII》全系列就拖了將近13年，如果真想要玩到這段劇情，可能要先擔心遊戲會不會爛尾吧嗚嗚～<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/01-2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F04%2F01-2.jpg&h=4933d78b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0abcf5135542846b3d39a17ea5cb726190cddbec","tid":1986034,"uid":71913,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T14:49:53.000Z","msg":"為愛鼓掌"},{"pid":"d5d1869db73eddade6c0e470deadf5c669654808","tid":1986034,"uid":189157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T14:56:02.000Z","msg":"tifa世界第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce5eacd9974fc2feab052afaba2c976725ac73e5","tid":1986034,"uid":25345,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T15:18:47.000Z","msg":"全部人睇哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c1953b74f079b35fbd6bfc54a3cb65b97942f36","tid":1986034,"uid":7609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T15:24:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3b0c9969ac476e7c40d58fc127870989624e184","tid":1986034,"uid":94835,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T15:46:45.000Z","msg":"原文對白好正常<br />\n你會唔會諗多咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7271c2cfeeda16cf641ff0a6fd3c7bbf87dbc15e","tid":1986034,"uid":25345,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c3b0c9969ac476e7c40d58fc127870989624e184","tid":1986034,"uid":94835,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T15:46:45.000Z","msg":"原文對白好正常<br />\n你會唔會諗多咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T16:17:38.000Z","msg":"作者話扑左"},{"pid":"20b662927e586aece3f223ddd7ece3942d8b3fe5","tid":1986034,"uid":60814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7271c2cfeeda16cf641ff0a6fd3c7bbf87dbc15e","tid":1986034,"uid":25345,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c3b0c9969ac476e7c40d58fc127870989624e184","tid":1986034,"uid":94835,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T15:46:45.000Z","msg":"原文對白好正常<br />\n你會唔會諗多咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T16:17:38.000Z","msg":"作者話扑左"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T17:02:33.000Z","msg":"點忍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"193c51f4e7d891b337dae2a9296bea425bf3eb4b","tid":1986034,"uid":16123,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T21:07:39.000Z","msg":"俾tifa拳打腳踢<br />\n最後黎個 胸斬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdef5b95800f16cddb3960588537c1b7705a5ccb","tid":1986034,"uid":176304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"193c51f4e7d891b337dae2a9296bea425bf3eb4b","tid":1986034,"uid":16123,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T21:07:39.000Z","msg":"俾tifa拳打腳踢<br />\n最後黎個 胸斬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T16:53:58.000Z","msg":"一野揸爆cloud 蛋蛋"}]}